	</li>
		
		
		
	
<li class="commentbody" id="comment-405247">
			<cite>Jen</cite>
						&nbsp;
			<a class="commentlink" href="#comment-405247" title="">July 12, 2010</a> 

		
			<div class="commentcount">65</div>

				<p>I just made this the other night, but I roasted it with the basil (instructions didn&#8217;t say what to do with it, so I put it on top of the tomatoes).  And once it was done, I added in a sliced roasted red onion, 2 small roasted zucchini &#8211; sliced, and some cooked ground Italian sausage.  It was delightful!  The sweetness of the roasted veggies against the slight tartness of cherry tomatoes &#8211; utterly addicting!</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
